      • getWindowObjectByJS

        public static java.lang.Object getWindowObjectByJS(org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver.Window window)
        Parameters:
        window - Selenium WebDriver Window object
        Returns:
        A browser window object returned by javascript, containing properties like height, clientWidth, pageXOffset etc.
        null, if some exception happens. PROPERTY_DRIVER_WINDOW=Window object if we can store it.
